09-19T05:08:14.000Z","msg":"前幾日去完 搭鐵去清涼里站轉itx去加平 <br />\n加平站出面有個觀光巴士 6000won全日任搭 南怡島站落再飛索入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"如果唔跟tour都想飛入去"},{"pid":"27edf19ac702b02c5fcaeaf5d4a1a23b0fe8aaa1","tid":1565503,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BHsEgCz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBHsEgCz.jpg&h=0f988e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我諗下次黎都係自己黎<br />\n跟tour南怡島連埋上落船得兩個鐘<br />\n如果鐘意影相建戲自己黎"},{"pid":"2a78f3dd970a14157f0b14c8ab2247611f016a80","tid":1565503,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db7257ef6144ebbe41e566fc2544304768876d0c","tid":1565503,"uid":140859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:08:14.000Z","msg":"前幾日去完 搭鐵去清涼里站轉itx去加平 <br />\n加平站出面有個觀光巴士 6000won全日任搭 南怡島站落再飛索入去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"itx使唔使早d買飛？？？"},{"pid":"e828dec113e5afcc5783177ef8c89659168dc7b4","tid":1565503,"uid":243455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"Join tour 跑3個景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />建議買定d小食係車食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上踩車<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cdsqyS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cdsqyS.png&h=9e1b67b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLunch果餐食<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0BxBFN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0BxBFN.png&h=846bdf21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚難食，不過預左<br />\n<br />\n南怡島 好多人<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mp84sNC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMp84sNC.png&h=423e1c8c&s={SIZE}\" />建議一落船直接奔入去，入面靚好多，無謂係入口同人迫，南怡島真心靚，可以hea成日。<br />\n<br />\n最尾去小法國村<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DnvKsNT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDnvKsNT.png&h=607fb34f&s={SIZE}\" />最廢嘅景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總括：如果join tour可以join2個景點踩車+南怡島就夠，留多d時間係南怡島玩仲好。<br />\n小法國村，如果去過濟洲果個小王子村可以唔使去呢個，勁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（利申：兩個都去過）"},{"pid":"b93d9a594d9ad34db0e767e3b978e0735031ed80","tid":1565503,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/19/152516_5d4c13b79b4a67673bfe975804583258.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F19%2F152516_5d4c13b79b4a67673bfe975804583258.JPG&h=1e2bec17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小法國村真係好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有一個鐘行，不如比多半粒鐘南怡島好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e9e688bb1b8d0ec4303353b87c7b184a7e0dc1","tid":1565503,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"晨靜樹木園唔知會唔會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2357b59afc3d673e3b4ac3dee407c3fef3b8a6","tid":1565503,"uid":140859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a78f3dd970a14157f0b14c8ab2247611f016a80","tid":1565503,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db7257ef6144ebbe41e566fc2544304768876d0c","tid":1565503,"uid":140859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:08:14.000Z","msg":"前幾日去完 搭鐵去清涼里站轉itx去加平 <br />\n加平站出面有個觀光巴士 6000won全日任搭 南怡島站落再飛索入去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"itx使唔使早d買飛？？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:47:33.000Z","msg":"我係喺清涼里站即場㩒機買"},{"pid":"b729fc29bc37238f4faba8a6cba3b6c4b3c3cfde","tid":1565503,"uid":324843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"其實如果想自己去南怡島, 可以係Klook/ kkday訂來回接駁巴士車票 (可買Package包門票&amp;船票)。接駁巴士(旅遊巴) 有得揀南大門/ 明洞新世界百貨上車&amp;落車, 直到目的地 &amp; 全程無導遊 (不過只得限定時間的班次, 而且回程3:30pm就要返去集合地等車)<br />\n<br />\n如果想去埋其他景點, 可以落車後自己搭加平觀光巴士 (如想撘回程車, 我諗頂盡去多1個景點, 不過應該都好趕)<br />\n<br />\n如果你想跑超過2個景點, 建議你 join local tour, 唔駛煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b1b38c9371b1ee6991f950453f05e8e8761b1a","tid":1565503,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"直接踩單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個島冇野做"},{"pid":"46927dc912281283da3d5e69cc7eb7d1757cec52","tid":1565503,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1b1b38c9371b1ee6991f950453f05e8e8761b1a","tid":1565503,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"直接踩單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個島冇野做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:14:54.000Z","msg":"鐘意影相 影銀杏同紅葉應該都可以影好耐"},{"pid":"82ddd7b2eb0e30465c540fe6c0195ce9d2f9c9b6","tid":1565503,"uid":101336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T01:10:46.000Z","msg":"早幾日去完<br />\n去程喺龍山坐itx到加平，之後坐第一班觀光巴士去南怡島渡口<br />\n<br />\n全日嘅行程:<br />\nitx-&gt;加平-&gt;南怡島-&gt;lunch-&gt;小法國村-&gt;晨靜樹木園-&gt;清平-&gt;地鐵<br />\n景點與景點之間都係坐觀光巴士<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己去嘅好處係鍾意行幾耐都得，我地每個景點都留咗成兩個鐘以上(小法國1.5hr)，影夠哂相先走<br />\n同埋因為我地早到南怡島(10點前)，比較少人，行得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐itx嘅話可以上網買定飛先，咁就唔怕買唔到飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}